    <item>
      <title>肖尔茨顾问预计德国经济明年将回升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/scholz-advisers-see-german-economy-picking-up-into-next-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨的独立专家小组表示，在家庭消费增强的支持下，德国经济将在未来几个月获得一些动力，尽管今年仍将勉强实现增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/scholz-advisers-see-german-economy-picking-up-into-next-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 12:30:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
